- Modules installed:
   - Cheerio
   - Checksum
   - Request-Promise


- Started with this tutorial: https://medium.freecodecamp.org/how-to-build-a-simple-search-bot-in-30-minutes-eb56fcedcdb1

- Diversions from this tutorial: not using a hash of the ingested HTML to return a true/false to see if there have been any changes

- Needed a browser-side module server, so installed Browserify

- Needed something that would automatically recompile your file when you make changes to it, so installed Beefy